Well to be honest BetaMage, when all we get are little snippets, half truths, rumors, and partial info about PoP, AND it is all things that look to the mage community to be subpar and lacking...what do you really expect?<br>
<br>
When VI decides to be open about upcoming changes instead of us relying on leaks and rumors, THEN they can ask for reasoned discussion.  When all we get to see is the apparent downsides while the upsides remain &quot;trust me&quot; issues, then outrage and upset people is what you are going to get.<br>
<br>
Reasoned discussion requires FACTS, all we have is speculation, so [VI] give us some facts to work with, and we will give you your feedback.<br>
